return ['x-generator'=>'GlotPress/4.0.3','translation-revision-date'=>'2025-10-29 18:58:07+0000','plural-forms'=>'nplurals=1; plural=0;','project-id-version'=>'Plugins - Contact Form 7 - Stable (latest release)','language'=>'zh_TW','messages'=>['Exclude a line from output if all of its mail-tags are blank'=>'在輸出內容中排除電子郵件標籤全部為空的那一行','With help from cloud-based machine learning, anti-spam services will protect your forms (<a href="%1$s">Cloudflare Turnstile</a>). Even payment services are natively supported (<a href="%2$s">Stripe</a>).'=>'使用雲端機器學習提供的協助，反垃圾訊息服務能保護網站的表單 (<a href="%1$s" target="_blank">Cloudflare Turnstile</a>)，甚至對付款服務也提供了原生支援 (<a href="%2$s" target="_blank">Stripe</a>)。','Contact Form 7 supports spam-filtering with <a href="%1$s">Akismet</a>. <a href="%2$s">Cloudflare Turnstile</a> blocks annoying spambots. Plus, using <a href="%3$s">disallowed list</a>, you can block messages containing specified keywords or those sent from specified IP addresses.'=>'Contact Form 7 支援 <a href="%1$s" target="_blank">Akismet</a> 進行垃圾訊息篩選，同時支援 <a href="%2$s" target="_blank">Cloudflare Turnstile</a> 封鎖惱人的垃圾訊息機器人。除此之外，使用<a href="%3$s" target="_blank">封鎖清單</a>可以阻止包含特定關鍵字或從特定 IP 位址傳送的電子郵件。','You can add customization code snippets here. For details, see <a href="%s">Additional settings</a>.'=>'請在這裡新增自訂程式碼片段。如需進一步了解詳細資訊，請參閱〈<a href="%s" target="_blank">其他設定</a>〉。','You can edit messages used in various situations here. For details, see <a href="%s">Editing messages</a>.'=>'請在這裡編輯使用於不同的情況的訊息。如需進一步了解詳細資訊，請參閱〈<a href="%s" target="_blank">編輯訊息</a>〉。','You can edit the email template here. For details, see <a href="%s">Setting up mail</a>.'=>'請在這裡編輯電子郵件範本。如需進一步了解詳細資訊，請參閱〈<a href="%s" target="_blank">設定電子郵件</a>〉。','You can edit the form template here. For details, see <a href="%s">Editing form template</a>.'=>'請在這裡編輯表單範本。如需進一步了解詳細資訊，請參閱〈<a href="%s" target="_blank">編輯表單範本</a>〉。','Contact form editor tabs'=>'聯絡表單編輯器分頁','https://github.com/rocklobster-in/'=>'https://github.com/rocklobster-in/','Rock Lobster Inc.'=>'Rock Lobster Inc.','Search results for: <strong>%s</strong>'=>'<strong>「%s」</strong>的搜尋結果','Turnstile validation failed.'=>'Turnstile 驗證失敗。','Turnstile token is empty.'=>'Turnstile 權杖為空。','Turnstile is active on this site.'=>'Turnstile 已在這個網站啟用。','Cloudflare Turnstile integration'=>'Cloudflare Turnstile 整合模組','Turnstile is Cloudflare&#8217;s smart CAPTCHA alternative, which confirms web visitors are real and blocks unwanted bots without slowing down web experiences for real users.'=>'Turnstile 是 Cloudflare 的智慧型人機驗證替代方案，可用來確認網站訪客是否為真人，並能在不減損真人使用者的網站體驗的狀況下，封鎖不需要的漫遊器。','<strong>Error:</strong> Invalid key values.'=>'<strong>錯誤:</strong> 無效的金鑰。','Turnstile'=>'Turnstile','The Constant Contact integration has been removed.'=>'Constant Contact 整合模組已移除。','API configuration cleared.'=>'API 組態已清除。','HTML Disallowance: %s'=>'不允許使用的 HTML 項目: %s','Invalid tag name (%s) is specified.'=>'無效的標籤名稱 (%s) 已指定。','Could not access filesystem.'=>'無法存取檔案系統。','Sender&#8217;s message failed to send'=>'寄件者的電子郵件傳送失敗','https://contactform7.com/turnstile-integration/'=>'https://contactform7.com/turnstile-integration/','<strong>Attention reCAPTCHA users:</strong> Google attempts to make all reCAPTCHA users migrate to reCAPTCHA Enterprise, meaning Google charges you for API calls exceeding the free tier. Contact Form 7 supports <a href="https://contactform7.com/turnstile-integration/">Cloudflare Turnstile</a>, and we recommend it unless you have reasons to use reCAPTCHA.'=>'<strong>Google reCAPTCHA 使用者注意事項:</strong> Google 計畫將全部 Google reCAPTCHA 使用者移轉至 reCAPTCHA Enterprise API，這代表 Google 對超過免費額度的 API 呼叫會收取費用。Contact Form 7 支援 <a href="https://contactform7.com/turnstile-integration/" target="_blank">Cloudflare Turnstile</a>，除非對 Google reCAPTCHA 有非用不可的原因，否則我們建議使用 Cloudflare Turnstile。','Contact Form 7 has completed the <a href="https://contactform7.com/2025/01/08/complete-removal-of-constant-contact-integration/">removal of the Constant Contact integration</a>. We recommend <a href="https://contactform7.com/sendinblue-integration/">Brevo</a> as an alternative.'=>'Contact Form 7<a href="https://contactform7.com/2025/01/08/complete-removal-of-constant-contact-integration/" target="_blank">已完整移除 Constant Contact 整合模組</a>。如果有類似功能需求，建議改用 <a href="https://contactform7.com/sendinblue-integration/" target="_blank">Brevo 整合模組</a>。','Add Contact Form'=>'新增聯絡表單','Invalid Stripe Payment Intent ID detected.'=>'偵測到無效的 Stripe Payment Intent ID。','https://contactform7.com/contributing/'=>'https://contactform7.com/contributing/','There are several ways for you to <a href="%s">contribute to the project</a>: testing, coding, translating it into your local languages, helping other users, financial donations, etc, etc. We equally welcome you regardless of the way you contribute.'=>'使用者有許多可以<a href="%s" target="_blank">貢獻這個專案</a>的方式: 測試、撰寫程式碼、將外掛本地化本地化為使用者的母語、協助其他使用者、捐款贊助等。無論是使用哪種方式貢獻，我們都同樣歡迎。','It is hard to continue to maintain this plugin without support from users like you.'=>'沒有各位使用者的支持，很難繼續維護這個外掛。','Generates a form-tag for a <a href="https://contactform7.com/text-fields/">multi-line plain text input area</a>.'=>'為<a href="https://contactform7.com/text-fields/" target="_blank">多行純文字輸入欄位區域</a>產生表單標籤。','Text area form-tag generator'=>'文字區域表單標籤產生程式','Text area'=>'文字區域','Generates a form-tag for a <a href="https://contactform7.com/text-fields/">telephone number input field</a>.'=>'為<a href="https://contactform7.com/text-fields/" target="_blank">電話號碼輸入欄位</a>產生表單標籤。','Telephone number field form-tag generator'=>'電話號碼欄位表單標籤產生程式','Telephone number field'=>'電話號碼欄位','Generates a form-tag for a <a href="https://contactform7.com/text-fields/">URL input field</a>.'=>'為<a href="https://contactform7.com/text-fields/" target="_blank">網址輸入欄位</a>產生表單標籤。','URL field form-tag generator'=>'網址欄位表單標籤產生程式','URL field'=>'網址欄位','Generates a form-tag for an <a href="https://contactform7.com/text-fields/">email address input field</a>.'=>'為<a href="https://contactform7.co