smet 已在這個網站啟用。','CAPTCHAs are designed to distinguish spambots from humans, and are therefore helpless against human spammers. In contrast to CAPTCHAs, Akismet checks form submissions against the global database of spam; this means Akismet is a comprehensive solution against spam. This is why we consider Akismet to be the centerpiece of the spam prevention strategy.'=>'CAPTCHA 人機驗證專門設計用來區分垃圾訊息機器人及真人，因此對於傳送垃圾訊息的真人束手無策。Akismet 與 CAPTCHA 不同，它會依據全球垃圾訊息資料庫檢查提交的表單資料，這代表 Akismet 是對抗垃圾訊息的全方位解決方案，這也是我們認為 Akismet 是垃圾訊息預防策略的主要核心。','Learn how your data is processed.'=>'進一步了解 Akismet 如何處理這個網站的資料','This form uses Akismet to reduce spam.'=>'這份聯絡表單使用 Akismet 減少垃圾訊息。','Contact form'=>'聯絡表單','Uploadable file size exceeds PHP&#8217;s maximum acceptable size.'=>'上傳檔案的大小超過 PHP 組態可接受的上限值。','Colons are used in form-tag names.'=>'表單標籤名稱中使用了冒號。','Please enter a telephone number.'=>'請輸入電話號碼。','Please enter a URL.'=>'請輸入網址。','Please enter an email address.'=>'請輸入電子郵件地址。','This field has a too large number.'=>'輸入這個欄位的數值太大。','This field has a too small number.'=>'輸入這個欄位的數值太小。','Please enter a number.'=>'請輸入數值。','This field has a too late date.'=>'輸入這個欄位的日期太晚。','This field has a too early date.'=>'輸入這個欄位的日期太早。','Please enter a date in YYYY-MM-DD format.'=>'請以 YYYY-MM-DD 的格式輸入日期。','The request payload format is not supported.'=>'不支援的要求承載格式。','Hook %1$s is <strong>deprecated</strong> since Contact Form 7 version %2$s with no alternative available.'=>'Contact Form 7 從 %2$s 版開始，%1$s 勾點<strong>已淘汰不用</strong>且不提供替代勾點。','The uploaded file is too large.'=>'上傳的檔案大小超過上限。','This field has a too short input.'=>'輸入這個欄位的內容太短。','This field has a too long input.'=>'輸入這個欄位的內容太長。','Please fill out this field.'=>'請填寫這個欄位。','Function %1$s is <strong>deprecated</strong> since Contact Form 7 version %2$s! Use %3$s instead.'=>'Contact Form 7 從 %2$s 版開始，%1$s 函式<strong>已淘汰不用</strong> ，請改用 %3$s。','Spam protection'=>'垃圾訊息保護','Function %1$s was called incorrectly. %2$s %3$s'=>'呼叫 %1$s 函式的方式不正確。%2$s %3$s','Hello,

