《%1$s》網站管理員','Opt-in confirmation from %s'=>'《%s》通知：確認加入','Complete payment'=>'完成付款','Proceed to checkout'=>'開始結帳','Payment is required. Please pay by credit card.'=>'必須付款。請以信用卡付款。','Payments'=>'付款服務','Publishable Key'=>'可發佈金鑰','Stripe is not available on this site. It requires an HTTPS-enabled site.'=>'Stripe 在這個網站無法提供服務，Stripe 需要已啟用 HTTPS 的網站。','Stripe is active on this site.'=>'Stripe 已在這個網站啟用。','Stripe integration'=>'Stripe 整合','Stripe is a simple and powerful way to accept payments online. Stripe has no setup fees, no monthly fees, and no hidden costs. Millions of businesses rely on Stripe&#8217;s software tools to accept payments securely and expand globally.'=>'Stripe 是易用且功能強大的線上收款方式。Stripe 不須設定費、不須繳交月費，也沒有隱藏費用。數以百萬計的企業依靠 Stripe 的軟體工具完成安全收款，並擴張他們的全球性業務。','personal name%1$s %2$s'=>'%1$s %2$s','Unique identifier for the contact form.'=>'聯絡表單的唯一識別碼。','Dots are used in form-tag names.'=>'表單標籤名稱中使用了句號。','Show welcome panel'=>'顯示 [歡迎使用] 面板','Welcome panel'=>'[歡迎使用] 面板','Stripe'=>'Stripe','https://contactform7.com/stripe-integration/'=>'https://contactform7.com/stripe-integration/','Your contact forms will become more powerful and versatile by integrating them with external APIs. With CRM and email marketing services, you can build your own contact lists (<a href="%s">Brevo</a>).'=>'透過整合外部 API，聯絡表單功能會更加強大及豐富；使用 CRM 及電子郵件行銷服務，便能建置專屬的聯絡清單 (<a href="%s" target="_blank">Brevo</a>)。','You have strong allies to back you up.'=>'提供支援的強大盟友','Integration with external APIs'=>'與外部 API 整合','https://contactform7.com/integration-with-external-apis/'=>'https://contactform7.com/integration-with-external-apis/','You can expand the possibilities of your contact forms by integrating them with external services. For details, see %s.'=>'網站管理員可以透過將聯絡表單整合外部服務，為聯絡表單擴充更多功能。如需進一步了解，請參閱〈%s〉。','Integration with External API'=>'整合外部 API','Manage your email templates'=>'管理電子郵件範本','You have no active email template yet.'=>'這個網站目前沒有使用中的電子郵件範本。','&mdash; Select &mdash;'=>'&mdash; 選取 &mdash;','Select an email template:'=>'選取電子郵件範本:','Send a welcome email to new contacts'=>'傳送給新聯絡人的歡迎電子郵件內容','Welcome email'=>'歡迎電子郵件','(opens in a new tab)'=>'(在新分頁中開啟)','Manage your contact lists'=>'管理聯絡人清單','You have no contact list yet.'=>'這個網站目前沒有聯絡人清單。','Select lists to which contacts are added:'=>'選取聯絡人要加入的清單:','Add form submitters to your contact lists'=>'將傳送表單的使用者加入這個網站的聯絡人清單','Contact lists'=>'聯絡人清單','You can set up the Brevo integration here. For details, see %s.'=>'網站管理員可以在這裡設定 Brevo 整合模組。如需進一步了解，請參閱〈%s〉。','Save changes'=>'儲存設定','API keysRemove key'=>'移除金鑰','API key'=>'API 金鑰','Setup integration'=>'設定整合模組','https://contactform7.com/sendinblue-integration/'=>'https://contactform7.com/sendinblue-integration/','Store and organize your contacts while protecting user privacy on Brevo, the leading CRM & email marketing platform in Europe. Brevo offers unlimited contacts and advanced marketing features.'=>'Brevo 是歐洲的 CRM 及電子郵件行銷平台領導廠商，可以使用保護使用者隱私權的方式儲存並整理聯絡人。Brevo 提供不限數量的聯絡人及進階行銷功能。','You have not been authenticated. Make sure the provided API key is correct.'=>'目前的連線並未通過驗證。請確認提供的 API 金鑰是否正確。','Failed to attach a file. The total file size exceeds the limit of 25 megabytes.'=>'無法附加檔案。檔案大小總計超過 25 MB 上限。','Failed to attach a file. %s is not a readable file.'=>'無法附加檔案。%s 不是可讀取的檔案。','Failed to attach a file. %s is not in the allowed directory.'=>'無法附加檔案。%s 不在允許的目錄中。','Submit'=>'傳送','(optional)'=>'(選填)','Disallowed words (%s) are used.'=>'封鎖的字詞 (%s) 已使用。','Disallowed words are used.'=>'封鎖的字詞已使用。','(This message was added in Contact Form 7 version %s.)'=>'(這個訊息於 Contact Form 7 %s 開始加入)','The fourth parameter ($mail_tag) must be an instance of the WPCF7_MailTag class.'=>'第 4 個參數 ($mail_tag) 必須是 WPCF7_MailTag 類別的執行個體。','g:i a'=>'a g:i','%1$s at %2$s'=>'%1$s %2$s','Error'=>'發生錯誤','The total size of attachment files is too large.'=>'附件檔案大小超過上限。','Unavailable HTML elements are used in the form template.'=>'在表單範本中採用了不可使用的 HTML 元素。','reCAPTCHA is active on this site.'=>'reCAPTCHA 已在這個網站啟用。','reCAPTCHA response token is empty.'=>'reCAPTCHA 回應權杖為空。','Submitted nonce is invalid.'=>'已傳送的單次有效隨機碼無效。','User-Agent string is unnaturally short.'=>'使用者代理程式字串太短。','reCAPTCHA score (%1$.2f) is lower than the threshold (%2$.2f).'=>'reCAPTCHA 分數 (%1$.2f) 低於臨界值 (%2$.2f)。','Akismet returns a spam response.'=>'Akismet 傳回垃圾訊息回應。','HTTP Response: %1$s %2$s %3$s from %4$s'=>'HTTP 回應: 回應碼: %1$s，回應訊息: %2$s，回應內容: %3$s，網址: %4$s','Save Changes'=>'儲存設定','reCAPTCHA protects you against spam and other types of automated abuse. With Contact Form 7&#8217;s reCAPTCHA integration module, you can block abusive form submissions by spam bots.'=>'reCAPTCHA 可以保護網站免受垃圾訊息及其他類型的自動化不當使用。使用 Contact Form 7 的 reCAPTCHA 整合模組，便能封鎖垃圾訊息機器人提交的無效表單。','reCAPTCHA (v3)'=>'reCAPTCHA (v3)','API keys for reCAPTCHA v3 are different from those for v2; keys for v2 do not work with the v3 API. You need to register your sites again to get new keys for v3. For details, see %s.'=>'reCAPTCHA v3 的 API 金鑰與 v2 不同，reCAPTCHA v3 無法使用 v2 的金鑰運作，因此必須為這個網站註冊一組 v3 的新金鑰。如需進一步了解，請參閱〈%s〉。','API keysRemove Keys'=>'移除金鑰','App Secret'=>'應用程式密碼','API Key'=>'API 金鑰','Constant Contact'=>'Constant Contact','Email marketing'=>'電子郵件行銷','It is not allowed to use files outside the wp-content directory.'=>'無法使用 wp-content 目錄之外的檔案。','Professional services'=>'專業服務','https://contactform7.com/custom-development/'=>'https://contactform7.com/custom-development/','Support forums'=>'技術支援論壇','https://wordpress.org/support/plugin/contact-form-7/'=>'https://wordpress.org/support/plugin/contact-form-7/','Here are some available options to help solve your problems.'=>'以下提供幾個方式，或能解決外掛使用上的問題。','Do you need help?'=>'有需要協助的地方嗎？','Condition'=>'同意方式說明','mail output for acceptance checkboxes%1$s: %2$s'=>'%1$s: %2$s','Not consented'=>'不同意','Consented'=>'同意','Sending mail has been aborted.'=>'傳送中的電子郵件已遭終止。','https://contactform7.com/editing-messages/'=>'https://contactform7.com/editing-messages/','https://contactform7.com/editing-form-template/'=>'https://contactform7.com/editing-form-template/','This contact form is available only for logged in users.'=>'這份聯絡表單僅供已登入的使用者填寫。','Deprecated settings are used.'=>'使用了不建議的設定。','To use CAPTCHA, you need %s plugin installed.'=>'如需使用 CAPTCHA 驗證功能，必須先安裝 %s 外掛。','There was an error deleting the contact form.'=>'刪除聯絡表單時發生錯誤。','You are not allowed to access the requested contact form.'=>'目前的登入身分沒有存取要求的聯絡表單的權限。','The requested contact form was not found.'=>'找不到你所要求的聯絡表單。','You are not allowed to create a contact form.'=>'目前的登入身分沒有建立聯絡表單的權限。','Cannot create existing contact form.'=>'無法建立現有聯絡表單。','You are not allowed to access contact forms.'=>'目前的登入身分沒有存取聯絡表單的權限。','Attachment file does not exist at %path%.'=>'附件檔案不存在於 %path% 中。','Invalid mailbox syntax is used in the %name% field.'=>'在 [%name%] 欄位中使用了無效的信箱語法。','Unavailable names (%names%) are used for form controls.'=>'在表單控制項中採用了不可使用的名稱。表單控制項名稱請參考%names%。','There are invalid mail header fields.'=>'無效的電子郵件標頭欄位。','HTML tags are used in a message.'=>'在電子郵件內容中使用 HTML 標籤。','Sender email address does not belong to the site domain.'=>'寄件者電子郵件地址與網站的網域不相符。','Invalid mailbox syntax is used.'=>'使用了無效的信箱語法。','There is a possible empty field.'=>'含有空白欄位。','%s configuration error detected'=>'偵測到 %s 項組態錯誤','There was an error saving the contact form.'=>'儲存聯絡表單時發生錯誤。','Hook %1$s is <strong>deprecated</strong> since Contact Form 7 version %2$s! Use %3$s instead.'=>'Contact Form 7 從 %2$s 版開始，%1$s 勾點<strong>已淘汰不用</strong> ，請改用 %3$s。','Install a message storage plugin before this happens to you. <a href="%s">Flamingo</a> saves all messages through contact forms into the database. Flamingo is a free WordPress plugin created by the same author as Contact Form 7.'=>'在發生這種狀況前，請為這個網站安裝個能夠儲存電子郵件的外掛。<a href="%s" target="_blank">Flamingo</a> 是由 Contact Form 7 開發者 Takayuki Miyoshi 所開發的免費 WordPress 外掛，可直接透過聯絡表單將所有電子郵件儲存到資料庫中。','Contact Form 7 does not store submitted messages anywhere. Therefore, you may lose important messages forever if your mail server has issues or you make a mistake in mail configuration.'=>'Contact Form 7 不會儲存已傳送的電子郵件，所以當電子郵件伺服器發生問題或電子郵件設定有了錯誤，便可能永久失去重要電子郵件。','Before you cry over spilt mail&#8230;'=>'在為錯發的電子郵件後悔之前...','https://contactform7.com/comment-blacklist/'=>'https://contactform7.com/comment-blacklist/','Spammers target everything; your contact forms are not an exception. Before you get spammed, protect your contact forms with the powerful anti-spam features Contact Form 7 provides.'=>'垃圾訊息業者不會放過任何目標，這個網站的聯絡表單也不例外。請在網站收到垃圾訊息前，使用 Contact Form 7 所提供的強大反垃圾訊息功能保護聯絡表單。','Getting spammed? You have protection.'=>'收到垃圾訊息？保護網站的完整解決方案就在這裡。','Multiple form controls are in a single label element.'=>'單一標籤元素中包含多個表單控制項。','FAQ about Configuration Validator'=>'組態驗證程式的常見問題集','https://contactform7.com/configuration-validator-faq/'=>'https://contactform7.com/configuration-validator-faq/','The answer to the quiz is incorrect.'=>'問答題的答案不正確。','There was an error uploading the file.'=>'上傳檔案時發生錯誤。','You are not allowed to upload files of this type.'=>'目前的登入身分沒有上傳這個檔案類型的權限。','There was an unknown error uploading the file.'=>'上傳檔案時發生未知錯誤。','You must accept the terms and conditions before sending your message.'=>'傳送電子郵件前，你必須接受條款及條件。','One or more fields have an error. Please check and try again.'=>'一或多個欄位發生錯誤。請檢查並重試。','There was an error trying to send your message. Please try again later.'=>'嘗試傳送電子郵件時發生錯誤。請稍後再試。','Thank you for your message. It has been sent.'=>'感謝你的留言，已將留言傳送給站務人員。','mail subject%1$s "%2$s"'=>'%2$s (由《%1$s》的聯絡表單傳送)','Misconfiguration leads to mail delivery failure or other troubles. Validate your contact forms now.'=>'組態錯誤會導致電子郵件傳送失敗或其他問題，請立即驗證這個網站的聯絡表單。','Validate Contact Form 7 Configuration'=>'驗證 Contact Form 7 的聯絡表單組態','https://contactform7.com/configuration-errors/'=>'https://contactform7.com/configuration-errors/','Configuration validation completed. No invalid contact form was found.'=>'組態驗證已完成，沒有無效的聯絡表單。','Configuration validation completed. %s invalid contact form was found.'=>'組態驗證已完成，找到 %s 份無效的聯絡表單。','Validate Configuration'=>'驗證組態','Validate %s contact form now'=>'立即驗證 %s 份聯絡表單','You are not allowed to validate configuration.'=>'目前的登入身分沒有驗證組態的權限。','https://contactform7.com/recaptcha/'=>'https://contactform7.com/recaptcha/','Secret Key'=>'密鑰','Site Key'=>'網站金鑰','Settings saved.'=>'設定已儲存。','Invalid key values.'=>'無效的金鑰。','reCAPTCHA'=>'reCAPTCHA','Just another contact form plugin. Simple but flexible.'=>'簡單靈活的聯絡表單外掛。','https://contactform7.com/'=>'https://contactform7.com/','Contact form %d'=>'聯絡表單 %d','text area'=>'文字區域','Akismet'=>'Akismet','Text field'=>'文字欄位','tel'=>'電話號碼','URL'=>'網址','email'=>'電子郵件地址','text'=>'文字','Telephone number that the sender entered is invalid'=>'寄件者輸入了無效的電話號碼','URL that the sender entered is invalid'=>'寄件者輸入了無效的連結','Email address that the sender entered is invalid'=>'寄件者輸入了無效的電子郵件地址','Label'=>'按鈕文字','Submit button'=>'傳送按鈕','submit'=>'傳送按鈕','drop-down menu'=>'下拉式選單','Questions and answers'=>'問題及答案','Quiz'=>'問答題','quiz'=>'問答題','Sender does not enter the correct answer to the quiz'=>'寄件者並未輸入問答題的正確答案','Slider'=>'滑桿','Spinbox'=>'微調方塊','Number field'=>'數值欄位','number'=>'數值','Number is larger than maximum limit'=>'數值高於最大值限制','Number is smaller than minimum limit'=>'數值低於最小值限制','Number format that the sender entered is invalid'=>'寄件者輸入了無效的數值格式','This contact form has file uploading fields, but the temporary folder for the files (%s) does not exist or is not writable. You can create the folder or change its permission manually.'=>'這份聯絡表單中包含了檔案上傳欄位，但是檔案的暫存資料夾 (%s) 不存在或無法寫入。請手動建立資料夾或修改資料夾權限設定以修正這個問題。','Acceptable file types'=>'可接受的檔案類型','file'=>'檔案上傳','Uploading a file fails for PHP error'=>'因 PHP 錯誤導致上傳失敗','Uploaded file is too large'=>'上傳的檔案大小超過上限','Uploaded file is not allowed for file type'=>'系統不接受上傳檔案的檔案類型','Uploading a file fails for any reason'=>'因不明原因導致上傳失敗','Max'=>'最大值','Min'=>'最小值','Range'=>'範圍','Default value'=>'預設值','Date field'=>'日期欄位','date'=>'日期','Date is later than maximum limit'=>'日期晚於最大值限制','Date is earlier than minimum limit'=>'日期早於最小值限制','Date format that the sender entered is invalid'=>'寄件者輸入了無效的日期格式','Wrap each item with a label element.'=>'將 label 元素套用至選項文字','Field type'=>'欄位類型','radio buttons'=>'選項按鈕','checkboxes'=>'核取方塊','This contact form contains CAPTCHA fields, but the necessary libraries (GD and FreeType) are not available on your server.'=>'這份聯絡表單中使用了 CAPTCHA 驗證欄位，但這個網站的伺服器並未提供必要的 GD 以及 FreeType 函式庫。','This contact form contains CAPTCHA fields, but the temporary folder for the files (%s) does not exist or is not writable. You can create the folder or change its permission manually.'=>'這份聯絡表單中使用了 CAPTCHA 驗證欄位，但是檔案的暫存資料夾 (%s) 不存在或無法寫入。請透過手動建立資料夾或修改資料夾權限設定以修正這個問題。','Your entered code is incorrect.'=>'目前輸入的認證碼不正確。','The code that sender entered does not match the CAPTCHA'=>'寄信者輸入的驗證碼與 CAPTCHA 提供的不相符','Insert Tag'=>'插入標籤','Class attribute'=>'類別屬性','ID attribute'=>'ID 屬性','Acceptance checkbox'=>'同意方式核取方塊','acceptance'=>'同意方式','<code>%1$s</code> property of a <code>WPCF7_ContactForm</code> object is <strong>no longer accessible</strong>. Use <code>%2$s</code> method instead.'=>'<strong>無法存取</strong> <code>WPCF7_ContactForm</code> 物件 <strong> 的 <code>%1$s</code> 屬性。請改用 <code>%2$s</code> 方法加以取代。','Untitled'=>'未命名','Contact Form'=>'聯絡表單','There is a field with input that is shorter than the minimum allowed length'=>'當輸入的字元長度低於預設值時','There is a field with input that is longer than the maximum allowed length'=>'當輸入的字元長度高於預設值時','There is a field that the sender must fill in'=>'當寄件者未填寫必填欄位時','There are terms that the sender must accept'=>'當寄件者必須接受相關條款時','Submission was referred to as spam'=>'系統判定送出的內容為垃圾郵件','Validation errors occurred'=>'發生驗證錯誤','Sender&#8217;s message was sent successfully'=>'寄件者的電子郵件已成功傳送','Message Body:'=>'電子郵件內文:','Subject: %s'=>'主旨: %s','From: %s'=>'寄件者: %s','Send'=>'傳送','Your message'=>'你的訊息','Your email'=>'你的電子郵件地址','Your name'=>'你的全名','Form-tag Generator: %s'=>'表單標籤產生程式: %s','For more information:'=>'進一步了解相關資訊:','Any information you provide will not be shared with service providers without your authorization.'=>'網站管理員所提供的任何資訊，未經當事人授權，不會分享給服務提供商。','You may need to first sign up for an account with the service that you plan to use. When you do so, you would need to authorize Contact Form 7 to access the service with your account.'=>'網站管理員必須先向計畫採用的服務註冊一個帳號。註冊成功後，請授權 Contact Form 7 以網站管理員的帳號存取該項服務。','On this screen, you can manage services that are available through Contact Form 7. Using API will allow you to collaborate with any services that are available.'=>'在這個畫面中，網站管理員可以透過 Contact Form 7 管理可用的服務。使用 API 可讓這個網站與任何可用的服務進行協同作業。','There are also special mail-tags that have specific names, but do not have corresponding form-tags. They are used to represent meta information of form submissions like the submitter&#8217;s IP address or the URL of the page.'=>'有些含有指定名稱的特殊電子郵件標籤，並沒有對應的表單標籤。這些特殊電子郵件標籤用於顯示傳送表單的中繼資訊，例如傳送表單的使用者的 IP 位址或頁面網址。','A mail-tag is also a short code enclosed in square brackets that you can use in every Mail and Mail (2) field. A mail-tag represents a user input value through an input field of a corresponding form-tag.'=>'電子郵件標籤就是用於 [電子郵件] 及 [電子郵件 (2)] 各個欄位中以方括弧括住的短代碼。電子郵件標籤透過對應的表單標籤輸入欄位，將使用者輸入的值顯示出來。','While form-tags have a comparatively complex syntax, you do not need to know the syntax to add form-tags because you can use the straightforward tag generator (<strong>Generate Tag</strong> button on this screen).'=>'雖然表單標籤具備相對複雜的語法，但製表者無須掌握新增表單標籤的語法，便可以透過簡單易用的標籤產生程式產生表單標籤。在這個畫面上，那一整列的按鈕代表不同類型的<strong>表單標籤產生程式</strong>。','A form-tag is a short code enclosed in square brackets used in a form content. A form-tag generally represents an input field, and its components can be separated into four parts: type, name, options, and values. Contact Form 7 supports several types of form-tags including text fields, number fields, date fields, checkboxes, radio buttons, menus, file-uploading fields, CAPTCHAs, and quiz fields.'=>'表單標籤就是用於表單內容中以方括弧括住的短代碼。表單標籤一般顯示為輸入欄位，其構成分為四個部分: 類型、名稱、選項及欄位的值。Contact Form 7 支援各種類型的表單標籤，包含文字欄位、數值欄位、日期欄位、核取方塊、選項按鈕、選單、檔案上傳欄位、CAPTCHA 驗證以及問答題欄位。','<strong>Additional Settings</strong> provides a place where you can customize the behavior of this contact form by adding code snippets.'=>'<strong>[其他設定]</strong> 提供了一個可以讓製表者新增程式碼片段以便自訂聯絡表單行為的欄位。','In <strong>Messages</strong>, you can edit various types of messages used for this contact form. These messages are relatively short messages, like a validation error message you see when you leave a required field blank.'=>'在 <strong>[訊息]</strong> 設定頁中，可以編輯用於該份聯絡表單的各項訊息。這些都是相對較短的訊息，類似使用者在必填欄位留空時看到的驗證錯誤訊息。','<strong>Mail (2)</strong> is an additional mail template that works similar to Mail. Mail (2) is different in that it is sent only when Mail has been sent successfully.'=>'<strong>[電子郵件 (2)]</strong> 是與 [電子郵件] 運作方式相仿的電子郵件範本。[電子郵件 (2)] 的不同處在於它只有在 [電子郵件] 範本的內容成功傳送後，才會進行傳送。','<strong>Mail</strong> manages a mail template (headers and message body) that this contact form will send when users submit it. You can use Contact Form 7&#8217;s mail-tags here.'=>'在 <strong>[電子郵件]</strong> 設定頁中，可管理使用者傳送表單後，聯絡表單會寄送給收件者的電子郵件範本 (即電子郵件標頭及內文)。製表者也可以在這裡使用 Contact Form 7 的電子郵件標籤。','<strong>Form</strong> is a content of HTML form. You can use arbitrary HTML, which is allowed inside a form element. You can also use Contact Form 7&#8217;s form-tags here.'=>'<strong>[表單]</strong> 設定頁儲存了 HTML 表單的內容。在這個設定頁中，製表者可以使用所有可用於 form 元素的 HTML 標籤，也可以使用 Contact Form 7 的表單標籤。','<strong>Title</strong> is the title of a contact form. This title is only used for labeling a contact form, and can be edited.'=>'<strong>[表單標題]</strong> 就是聯絡表單的標題。表單標題僅用於標示聯絡表單，且可隨時進行編輯。','On this screen, you can edit a contact form. A contact form is comprised of the following components:'=>'在這個畫面中，製表者可以編輯聯絡表單。每份聯絡表單均由以下項目所組成:','<strong>Duplicate</strong> - Clones that contact form. A cloned contact form inherits all content from the original, but has a different ID.'=>'<strong>[複製]</strong> 功能 - 複製聯絡表單。複製出來的聯絡表單包含了來源聯絡表單的所有內容，僅有表單 ID 不同。','<strong>Edit</strong> - Navigates to the editing screen for that contact form. You can also reach that screen by clicking on the contact form title.'=>'<strong>[編輯]</strong> 功能 - 瀏覽至聯絡表單的編輯畫面。製表者也可以點擊聯絡表單的標題進入編輯畫面。','Hovering over a row in the contact forms list will display action links that allow you to manage your contact form. You can perform the following actions:'=>'將游標暫留於聯絡表單清單任一列上，便會顯示管理聯絡表單的操作連結。製表者可以進行以下操作:','On this screen, you can manage contact forms provided by Contact Form 7. You can manage an unlimited number of contact forms. Each contact form has a unique ID and Contact Form 7 shortcode ([contact-form-7 ...]). To insert a contact form into a post or a text widget, insert the shortcode into the target.'=>'在這個畫面中，可以管理 Contact Form 7 所提供的聯絡表單，且無管理數量限制。每份聯絡表單均包含唯一 ID 及 Contact Form 7 短代碼 ([contact-form-7 ...])。如需在文章或文字小工具中插入聯絡表單，將對應的短代碼插入適當位置即可。','Mail-tags'=>'電子郵件標籤','Form-tags'=>'表單標籤','Available Actions'=>'可進行的操作','Overview'=>'概觀','https://contactform7.com/additional-settings/'=>'https://contactform7.com/additional-settings/','File attachments'=>'檔案附件','Use HTML content type'=>'使用 HTML 內容類型','Message body'=>'電子郵件內文','Additional headers'=>'其他標頭','Subject'=>'主旨','From'=>'寄件者','To'=>'收件者','In the following fields, you can use these mail-tags:'=>'在下方欄位中，可以使用以下電子郵件標籤:','Mail (2) is an additional mail template often used as an autoresponder.'=>'[電子郵件 (2)] 是另一個電子郵件範本，通常用於自動回覆指定訊息給送出表單的使用者。','Use Mail (2)'=>'使用 [電子郵件 (2)]','Mail (2)'=>'電子郵件 (2)','Y/m/d'=>'Y/n/j','Edit &#8220;%s&#8221;'=>'編輯〈%s〉','Edit'=>'編輯','Date'=>'日期','Author'=>'製表者','Shortcode'=>'短代碼','Title'=>'表單標題','Additional Settings'=>'其他設定','Additional Settings (%d)'=>'其他設定 (%d)','Messages'=>'訊息','Mail'=>'電子郵件','Form'=>'表單','Support'=>'技術支援','https://contactform7.com/support/'=>'https://contactform7.com/support/','FAQ'=>'常見問題集','https://contactform7.com/faq/'=>'https://contactform7.com/faq/','Docs'=>'線上說明文件','https://contactform7.com/docs/'=>'https://contactform7.com/docs/','Delete'=>'刪除','Duplicate'=>'複製','Status'=>'狀態','You can also use this old-style shortcode:'=>'同時也可以使用舊式短代碼:','Copy this shortcode and paste it into your post, page, or text widget content:'=>'將下方的短代碼複製至這個網站的文章、頁面或文字小工具中:','Enter title here'=>'請在這裡輸入聯絡表單標題','Save'=>'儲存','You are not allowed to edit this contact form.'=>'目前的登入身分沒有編輯這份聯絡表單的權限。','https://contactform7.com/save-submitted-messages-with-flamingo/'=>'https://contactform7.com/save-submitted-messages-with-flamingo/','Spam filtering with Akismet'=>'使用 Akismet 篩選垃圾訊息','https://contactform7.com/spam-filtering-with-akismet/'=>'https://contactform7.com/spam-filtering-with-akismet/','https://contactform7.com/setting-up-mail/'=>'https://contactform7.com/setting-up-mail/','Contact Form 7 needs your support.'=>'Contact Form 7 需要你的支持。','Dismiss'=>'關閉','<strong>Contact Form 7 %1$s requires WordPress %2$s or higher.</strong> Please <a href="%3$s">update WordPress</a> first.'=>'<strong>Contact Form 7 %1$s 版需要 WordPress %2$s 版或更新版本</strong>，請先<a href="%3$s">更新 WordPress</a>。','Settings'=>'設定','Contact form deleted.'=>'聯絡表單已刪除。','Contact form saved.'=>'聯絡表單已儲存。','Contact form created.'=>'聯絡表單已建立。','Search Contact Forms'=>'搜尋聯絡表單','Error in deleting.'=>'刪除時發生錯誤。','You are not allowed to delete this item.'=>'目前的登入身分沒有刪除這個項目的權限。','You are not allowed to edit this item.'=>'目前的登入身分沒有編輯這個項目的權限。','Integration'=>'整合','Contact Forms'=>'聯絡表單','Edit Contact Form'=>'編輯聯絡表單','Contact'=>'聯絡表單','Contact Form 7'=>'Contact Form 7']];